advisories.title: Amazon Linux 2023 - ALAS2023-2023-407: Low priority package update for glibc
advisories.description:
Package updates are available for Amazon Linux 2023 that fix the following vulnerabilities:
CVE-2023-5156:
	A flaw was found in the GNU C Library. A recent fix for CVE-2023-4806 introduced the potential for a memory leak, which may result in an application crash.
